    <item>
      <title>芬兰称中国只需一个电话就能结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/russia-ukraine-china-can-end-war-with-a-phone-call-finland-s-stubb-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰总统亚历山大·斯塔布称，俄罗斯对中国的依赖已经达到了这样的程度，只要北京愿意，它完全可以结束乌克兰战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/russia-ukraine-china-can-end-war-with-a-phone-call-finland-s-stubb-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费案为何陷入法律困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/why-scotus-immunity-ruling-put-trump-s-hush-money-conviction-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于最高法院于 7 月 1 日就总统豁免权作出了具有里程碑意义的裁决，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 因伪造商业记录掩盖性丑闻而被控 34 项重罪，但这一判决目前仍悬而未决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/why-scotus-immunity-ruling-put-trump-s-hush-money-conviction-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:38:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍里斯·约翰逊出人意料地采取最后行动，避免保守党被彻底击败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/boris-johnson-makes-surprise-late-move-to-avert-tory-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲍里斯·约翰逊 (Boris Johnson) 周二晚间意外出现在竞选活动中，呼吁保守党选民阻止工党在英国大选中获得压倒性胜利，这是里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党为避免周四投票中出现预计的巨大损失而做出的最后一搏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/boris-johnson-makes-surprise-late-move-to-avert-tory-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
