      <title>减肥药涨价让拜登有机会重新发起攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-02/ozempic-costs-give-biden-opening-after-trump-debate-stumble</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，关于首都的金钱、权力和政治的时事通讯。今天，国家医疗保健记者 Riley Griffin 解释了为什么总统乔·拜登和参议员伯尼·桑德斯的一篇专栏文章导致诺和诺德和礼来股价暴跌。在这里注册并关注我们 @bpolitics。在这里给我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-02/ozempic-costs-give-biden-opening-after-trump-debate-stumble</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:54:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国正在为俄罗斯制造和测试致命攻击无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情的欧洲官员称，中国和俄罗斯公司正在研发一种类似于伊朗部署在乌克兰的攻击无人机，这一迹象表明北京方面可能正接近提供西方官员警告的那种致命援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>帕克称，泄露的民主党民意调查备忘录显示拜登支持率暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-plummets-in-leaked-democratic-polling-memo-puck-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新闻网站 Puck 周二发布的一份民意调查泄露备忘录显示，总统乔·拜登在上周的辩论中表现出色后，支持率暴跌，出现近三年来“最大的单周跌幅”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-plummets-in-leaked-democratic-polling-memo-puck-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞在法国大选中面临艰难斗争以获得多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-s-path-to-power-narrows-in-french-game-of-election-chess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟正试图战胜那些使出老招数阻止极右翼在周日最后一轮立法选举中掌权的对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-s-path-to-power-narrows-in-french-game-of-election-chess</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:56:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将与州长会面并接受采访以平息抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登本周计划会见民主党州长和议员，前往两个战场州，并接受自辩论表现糟糕以来的首次电视采访，试图安抚焦虑的支持者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2024 年竞选总统期间的法律案件时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普正在竞选重返白宫，同时面临多项迫在眉睫的刑事和民事审判——这是美国历史上其他候选人从未面临过的挑战。这些法律时间表有助于理解这一切]]></description>
